snippet.textDisplay:
Listening this helps memorizing names of Allah faster. Narrated Abu Huraira (RA): Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) said, "Allah has ninety-nine names, i.e. one-hundred minus one, and whoever knows them will go to Paradise." Sahih al-Bukhari 2736

Narrated Abu Huraira(RA): Allah has ninety-nine Names, i.e., one hundred minus one, and whoever believes in their meanings and acts accordingly, will enter Paradise; and Allah is witr (one) and loves 'the witr' (i.e., odd numbers). Sahih al-Bukhari 6410
